le maupun promosi.\", \"link_page\": \"video-production.video-animasi\", \"link_youtube\": \"https://www.youtube.com/embed/xC4ze0p0b5Y\"}, {\"id\": \"631b3bf86c560\", \"judul\": \"Video Konten Sosmed\", \"gambar\": \"631b3bf86a4af-220909.jpg\", \"deskripsi\": \"Pembuatan video untuk konten posting maupun promosi di social media seperti Youtube, TikTok, maupun Instagram.\", \"link_page\": \"video-production.video-konten-sosmed\", \"link_youtube\": \"https://www.youtube.com/embed/xC4ze0p0b5Y\"}, {\"id\": \"631b3c1910e6f\", \"judul\": \"Video Company Profile\", \"gambar\": \"631b3c190ee7c-220909.jpg\", \"deskripsi\": \"Pembuatan video company profile untuk meningkatkan image perusahaan yang mendukung promosi bisnis.\", \"link_page\": \"video-production.video-company-profile\", \"link_youtube\": \"https://www.youtube.com/embed/xC4ze0p0b5Y\"}]', '2022-09-09 11:52:02', '2022-09-09 19:56:49');

